headline.print_headline: Ukraine Charts Course to Europe, Wants Better Russia Ties
headline.main: Ukraine Charts Course to Europe, Wants Better Russia Ties

lead_paragraph: Acting President Oleksander Turchinov said on Sunday Ukraine would try to improve relations with Russia but made clear that Kiev's return to European integration would be the priority.
